data.description: Move in by May 7 and receive a $50 Amazon Gift Card Another hot home offered by Sapir Realty is available for rent! We pride ourselves on our customer service because we know that our customers are at the heart of our company. With a newly redesigned website and assistance around the clock, applying online has never been easier. We recognize that utilizing technology does not diminish the importance of human interaction, which is why real team members are always just a phone call away to answer your every question. Tour this property today or skip right to it and apply now! Unique property features: - Fresh Paint - Entire Hardwood flooring - Spacious and tiled bathroom - Wide parking area - Furnished Kitchen with modern Appliances and granite countertop Disclosure: All information is believed to be accurate, however, changes to the exterior, interior, landscaping, or appliances may have occurred since the photographs were taken, and prices and dates may change without notice. Sapir Realty does not lease homes through Craigslist nor do we accept payment of deposits via CashApp, Zelle, or Wire transfers. Beware of scammers. Please make sure to call our office to confirm payment options.
